questionText:
This question is about the LENGTH OF YOUR MENSTRUAL CYCLE. Many women have a 28 day cycle but many others have cycles that are shorter or longer. A menstrual cycle starts on the first day of your period and ends on the last day before your next period.
Given this way of calculating the length of a cycle, estimate the typical length of your cycle as accurately as possible. If you are not sure, make your best guess.
